{"tid":380883,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"堅尼：碧咸雲佬現在能值10億，傑斯20億！","createTime":"2017-08-30T13:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T13:13:34.000Z","uid":8968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0d39e6ceea2357eec3ba05b6f4706920cbb60a5","tid":380883,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:00:26.000Z","msg":"　　今年夏天轉會市場上的球員身價屢創新高，這讓曼聯名宿堅尼非常吃驚。<br />\n　　<br />\n瘋狂的轉會市場讓堅尼很震驚，「現在球員們的身價真的令人難以置信。這不是球員的問題，這是市場因素。很多實力一般的球員都要價3500萬英鎊，我的上帝，而真正出色的球員更是賣出天價。」<br />\n　　<br />\n堅尼接著表示，「如果放到現在，<span style=\"color: red;\">雲尼斯達萊將價值10億英鎊，大衛碧咸，也是10億，傑斯，20億英鎊！</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我自己？375萬英鎊，哈哈</span>。」堅尼在1993年從諾定咸森林轉會到曼聯時的身價就是375萬英鎊，當時已經創造了英超轉會費紀錄。"},{"pid":"24fd13461560cab663ba6cf7fbf0cb3878fbd4f0","tid":380883,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:01:07.000Z","msg":"賓斯馬夠10億啦"},{"pid":"c7c94b1f75520c15c3f8edd1e6bc6a45cc5f010e","tid":380883,"uid":10975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賓斯馬夠10億啦</blockquote><br />\n上場臨完場一腳射撚走賤種2分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n10億？有人買就係..."},{"pid":"89958c3f43d5675e892e2e534af5cad9e33fdfc7","tid":380883,"uid":54025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:07:46.000Z","msg":"碧咸依d無速度無扭波既鳩斬仔，今時今日應該上唔到位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3ohzAH4tGyDZasUzF6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3ohzAH4tGyDZasUzF6%2Fgiphy.gif&h=f8565989&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"618021e1b6582b267b5d5a6eb73f2f61024a1a4c","tid":380883,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:08:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>賓斯馬夠10億啦</blockquote><br />\n上場臨完場一腳射撚走賤種2分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n10億？有人買就係...</blockquote><br />\n10億都唔撚賣"},{"pid":"28ceaab51149daeb2715